# Project Structure

This is a Next.js application using Payload CMS and tRPC.

- **Next.js App Router:** The main application structure is defined in [`src/app/`](mdc:src/app).
- **Payload CMS Configuration:** Payload CMS is configured in [`src/payload.config.ts`](mdc:src/payload.config.ts).
- **Payload Collections:** CMS collections are defined under [`src/collections/`](mdc:src/collections).
- **Payload Generated Types:** Types generated by Payload are in [`src/payload-types.ts`](mdc:src/payload-types.ts).
- **Reusable Components:** UI components are located in [`src/components/`](mdc:src/components).
- **tRPC Setup:** tRPC client and server setup can be found in [`src/trpc/`](mdc:src/trpc).
- **Utility Functions:** Helper functions and utilities are in [`src/lib/`](mdc:src/lib).
- **Custom Hooks:** React hooks are defined in [`src/hooks/`](mdc:src/hooks).
- **Next.js Configuration:** Next.js specific configuration is in [`next.config.mjs`](mdc:next.config.mjs).
- **TypeScript Configuration:** Base TypeScript configuration is in [`tsconfig.json`](mdc:tsconfig.json).
